<div id="quote">
	<i>"If only your Corpse-Emperor could see his Imperium now, he would reel in disgust at what it has become."</i><br>
	<b>~Corradin Corvandro</b>
</div><br>

	<br><br>

<details open="open"><summary class="section-head">Appearance</summary>

	Corradin Corvandro is an imposing figure, clad in a striking full suit of black Power Armor adorned with intricate gold trimmings. The armor prominently displays the Sigil of the Black Legion on the right shoulder plate, while an array of bones is scattered across its surface, adding an air of dread.<br><br>

Typically, Corradin wears a heavily modified helm, featuring a faceplate that resembles a menacing skull, fused with a jagged crown of spikes that enhances his fearsome appearance.<br><br>

<br></br>



</details><br>

<details open="open"><summary class="section-head">Personality</summary>

	Corradin Corvandro, once a revered Captain of the Luna Wolves, has transformed into a formidable Chaos Lord of the Ashen Horde, serving the enigmatic and all-consuming power of Chaos Undivided. His armor, once gleaming with the silver and blue of his chapter, now bears the charred and ashen hues of his new allegiance. Corradin's personality is a blend of cunning and ferocity; he commands both fear and respect from his followers. No longer bound by the honor and discipline of the Imperium, he revels in the chaos of battle, seeing conflict as a means of personal evolution and a testament to his newfound power.<br><br>

Driven by an insatiable hunger for dominance, he orchestrates brutal campaigns against the enemies of Chaos, believing that only through total annihilation can he achieve true transcendence. His charisma, twisted and dark, draws the disillusioned and the desperate to his banner, forming a horde that embodies chaos in every sense. Corradin's tactical genius, honed during his days as a Captain, now manifests in ruthless ambushes and brutal skirmishes, where he embraces the unpredictability of war. He often engages in dark rituals, seeking to channel the energies of the warp, enhancing his already formidable combat prowess. Under his leadership, the Ashen Horde is not merely a band of marauders; it is a relentless force of destruction, driven by the will of Chaos itself, and Corradin stands at the center of this maelstrom, embodying the very essence of the dark gods he serves.<br></br>

<br></br>

</details><br>

